Acquisition test Scenario used for testing data acquisition. The signal quality should always be checked before training. You can monitor signals from electrodes used by SSVEP scenarios : CPz, POz, Oz, Iz, O1 and O2. Individual signals are shown for each channel, as well as output of the two spatial filters used and the FFT of the average of all channels.
